sources.title: Airbag 1997 Karra Elejalde Fernando Guillen Cuervo Alberto San Juan Maria De Med
sources.description: Spanish variation on the lost ring during bachelor party theme. Wonderfully odd movie with car crashes, A Team Shooting (lots of bullets, not much damage), hookers, references to religion and an opening game of eating dangerous amulets. Airbags play a role but I'll be damned if I can figure it out. English subtitles included in file.
